    "causal_summary": "Autonomous codebase-context-gathering loop that sweeps a feature's scope with a heterogeneous pool of models in parallel, merges their findings by cross-executor agreement, and converges on relevance-gated coverage saturation. It matters because it produces a verified reuse-first Context Report before planning and implementation, so existing code is extended rather than rewritten and stale or bloated context is avoided.",
